docs.title: prefect-dbt-flow
docs.text: Welcome to the prefect-dbt-flow integration repository! This project aims to provide a seamless integration for simplifying the execution of dbt workflows using Prefect.

docs.title: Requirements
docs.text: Before you get started, make sure you have the following prerequisites installed on your system: * dbt * prefect

docs.title: Setup
docs.text:
Follow these simple steps to set up the prefect-dbt-flow integration on your local machine: 1. Clone this repository to your local machine using the following command: 

git clone https://github.com/datarootsio/prefect-dbt-flow.git

  1. Initialize the prefect-dbt-flow integration by running: 
    prefect-dbt-flow init

docs.title: Get started
docs.text: To start using the prefect-dbt-flow integration, please refer to the documentation or follow the examples provided in the DEMO section.

docs.title: Changelog
docs.text: Keep track of changes, updates, and new features in the changelog file.

docs.title: Contributing
